        Create a new BetweenRestriction Object (to be used with ObjectFields). ObjectField values must be supplied in the order fieldLowerValue <= fieldHigherValue
        Parameters:
        field - ObjectField to build the restriction on
        fieldLowerValue - lower ObjectField value (must be numerical or Date)
        fieldHigherValue - higher ObjectField value (must be numerical or Date)
